          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "value": "GamesCom, Showing Off Our Big Chinned Baby"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "All of Hello Games stood surrounding the booth, positions taken up, ready for the first wave of attendees to careen around the corner and sploosh their inquisitive faces into the screens."
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "What began as a trickle soon escalated to a full-scale typhoon. By the early afternoon, the humidity was ridiculous, made all the more oppressive by the swarming mass of liquid human bearing down on us."
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "The attendees were the sea, and the booth was a ship; everyone would have to pull together to keep this baby afloat. There would be time for the odd sea shanty and some tomfoolery - perhaps even some shenanigans and the occasional jape. This would be the hardest week, but it would be an experience that brought everyone closer together."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
